= Chiwei Yan 鄢驰为

== Research
=== Interests

*Large-scale Optimization, Robust Optimization, Transportation and Logistics, Revenue Management, Computational Social Choice*

=== Submitted Papers

- *Yan, C., Swaroop, P., Ball, M.O., Barnhart, C. and Vaze, V., [http://papers.ssrn.com/abstract=2746568 Applying Majority Judgment over a Polyhedral Candidate Space], under revision for resubmission to /Management Science/, 2016.*
  -- Earlier version of this paper won Honorable Mention in 2012 INFORMS Public Sector Operations Research Best Paper Competition.

